{"tid":440903,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【暴動案】控方結案陳辭：首被告認襲警 應考慮非品格良好 提升犯罪傾向","createTime":"2017-10-19T07:56:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-21T12:25:25.000Z","uid":51904,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"613827c71cc16a4f36e6cc366ac7e35d0da7de75","tid":440903,"uid":51904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T07:56:41.000Z","msg":"去年農曆年初二發生的警民大衝突，涉案9人否認暴動、刑事毀壞等罪名，案件經歷4個半月審訊後，今日開始結案陳辭。控方首先指出，任職侍應的首被告審訊前承認襲警，法官在處理他餘下4項控罪時，應考慮他並非品格良好人士，酌情下調可信性或提升其犯罪傾向性。<br />\n<br />\n旺角大衝突中9人被控暴動案今結案陳辭，代表控方的副刑事檢控專員梁卓然指出，只要有3人或以上集結在一起，作出破壞社會安寧的行為，便構成暴動。梁根據案例，指若有人的生命財產受損害，或擔心其生命財產受損害，便構成「破壞社會安寧」。梁進一步指，若有人在案中的角色只是掘磚，但其行為與其他集結人士構成集體性，所以也應被視作參與暴動。<br />\n<br />\n案中首被告侍應莫嘉濤面臨3項暴動罪，及因破壞警車被控1項刑事毀壞罪，莫在審訊前已承認1項襲警罪。梁卓然根據上訴庭案例，指他已經認罪，法官裁決時不應把他當成一個品格良好人士來看待，應酌情下調可信性或提升其犯罪傾向性。審訊繼續。<br />\n<br />\n案中其他被告為清潔工鍾志華、演員何錦森、侍應霍廷昊、無業陳和祥、運輸工鄧敬宗、無業李卓軒、冷氣學徒林永旺及冷氣技工葉梓豐，年齡介乎18至71歲。"},{"pid":"3afb74437c6d59b6cc7c38ca9e0dec4b52a69bfe","tid":440903,"uid":46644,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T08:03:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5c08244fb912b2f689ba8e0ae62cb174b6645653","tid":440903,"uid":36551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T08:07:30.000Z","msg":"律政司就2014年「重奪公民廣場」一案向上訴庭提出對「雙學三子」加刑，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">副刑事檢控專員梁卓然</span></span>指3人雖沒直接使用暴力，但非法集結後果嚴重，事件中有保安受傷，又批評3人根本做不到「和理非」，指重奪公民廣場中的<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">「奪」字已有暴力意味</span></span>。梁指3名被告應即時監禁，緩刑及社會服務令均不適合。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170809&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=57059813\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170809%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D57059813&d=awM1WCYJ6JNa6LRpoiqvWjCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=3154443c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170809%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D57059813&h=3c027a25\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170809&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=57059813</a><br />\n<br />\n又係依條撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.mingpaocanada.com/VAN/ftp/News/20150401/HK/_01GN008_.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mingpaocanada.com%2FVAN%2Fftp%2FNews%2F20150401%2FHK%2F_01GN008_.jpg&h=0cc9f95c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"18a8807d2faff021bcff82ddfc7e5a472e2f1072","tid":440903,"uid":50533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T08:24:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ee90260bf018aa0638d03d67aa4b1972fd440411","tid":440903,"uid":46644,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T08:25:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1e051e1c86c46c37d1dda9f3b273255ea25c94eb","tid":440903,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T08:35:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">站務台投訴三色貓</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/430728/page/1?ref=android\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/430728/page/1?ref=android</a>"},{"pid":"dcc0bce34c0a344d4e3db7f99a3288ded3b10311","tid":440903,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T08:35:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">站務台投訴法國佬巫斯義</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/431997/page/1?ref=android\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/431997/page/1?ref=android</a>"},{"pid":"0b4b1f5fd9b5ecd867fce54b507bd184c1d0e647","tid":440903,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T08:42:38.000Z","msg":"Oct 17近期活躍五毛<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1三色貓</span></span><br />\n2群龍共舞<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">3法國佬巫斯義=香港鍵國</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;